OL,5, Barristers in England and Wales are    
OL,6, starting an indefinite, uninterrupted  
OL,7, strike, in an escalation of industrial 
OL,8, action over pay which began in April.  
OL,10,FThe Criminal Bar Association (CBA)     
OL,11,Fwalkout is likely to worsen existing   
OL,12,Fcourt delays, with tens of thousands of
OL,13,Fcases already waiting to go to trial.  
OL,15,FThe CBA wants a 25% rise in legal aid  
OL,16,Ffees for representing defendants who   
OL,17,Fcould not otherwise afford lawyers.    
OL,19,FJustice Minister Sarah Dines has called
OL,20,Fthe escalation "irresponsible".        
